    "Description": {
      "type": "text",
      "dtype": "String",
      "label": "Metapower Description",
      "value": "<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Gravitational Anchor grants you unprecedented control over an individual&rsquo;s gravitational force towards the ground. By manipulating the gravitational force acting upon a target, you can effectively immobilize them or alternatively diminish the momentum of their movements. Thrown projectiles might lose their velocity, strikes may lack impact, and even those in freefall may find themselves dragged down. This power grants you mastery over motion itself, akin to a conductor guiding a symphony of celestial forces.&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Increases Willpower by +5% per level\">Determined</abbr>&nbsp;activations may extend Gravitational Anchor&rsquo;s reach and the number and maximum weight of targets. However, the delicacy of this power is matched only by its potential dangers, as excessive manipulation could leave the Controller themselves feeling burdened by the very forces they wield.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
    },
